                <h3>Gobhi Manchurian</h3>
                <p>Gobi Manchurian is a popular Indo-Chinese dish made from cauliflower florets that are coated in a spicy batter and deep-fried until crispy. The fried cauliflower is then tossed in a flavorful sauce made from soy sauce, chili sauce, garlic, and ginger. It's garnished with chopped spring onions and sometimes sesame seeds. Gobi Manchurian is known for its spicy, tangy, and slightly sweet flavor.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;100</p>
                <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span>  
            </div>
        </div>
