        <div class="card">
            <img src="imagessouth/starters/Idli chaat.jpeg" alt="idli">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Idli Chaat</h3>
                <p>Idli Chaat is a creative twist on the traditional South Indian idli. It involves pan-frying or shallow frying bite-sized idli pieces until they become crispy on the outside. These fried idlis are then topped with various toppings such as chopped onions, tomatoes, cilantro, sev (crunchy chickpea noodles), sweet chutney, and spicy chutney. Idli Chaat is a fusion snack that combines the softness of idli with the crunchiness of chaat.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;60</p>
                <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span>  
            </div>
        </div>
